{"tid":1610372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一場為香港而打既仗 以後叫句：For Hong Kong","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T18:13:51.000Z","uid":262997,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb0475c81032f1d841b12b66090050c013435eb","tid":1610372,"uid":262997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"我地係邊個，或者到最後比人拉撚左都冇人知道，但宜三個月，係我地覺醒既開始，以後每場仗，我地係為香港而打。<br />\n<br />\n每場仗，我地都要話比自己知，我地想贏，我地希望贏，咁我地以後每場仗，都要打得團結啲，一致啲，有目的啲。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（攻型前線）</span></span><br />\n：前線有遮有汽油彈，試下主動進攻，<br />\n諗下霸左位置之後點樣守得好/延長戰線/諗下啲狗要攻我地會邊度攻，block撚住啲位/盡可能44陣（四個四個行事）<br />\ne.g. 車胎陣，試下疊高啲雜物疊到難拆啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（防型前線）</span></span><br />\n：前線助攻，盡可能一堆堆移動，目的不被打散；<br />\n當前線同大隊分得太開，就要盡可能幫補前面，盡可能快速K.O.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">（投擲師）</span></span><br />\n：水彈教學都教過好多次，落顏料、墨水、雞蛋⋯⋯落乜柒都好，擲過去啲狗度，總有一兩粒中佢地頭盔，<span style=\"color: gold;\">盲撚左既狗點都易打啲</span><br />\n《整法：麵粉加水入落氣球度，再綁結就ok》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（旗手+哨兵+吹哨子）</span></span><br />\n：重要到每次都要提，企後面啲人可能根本乜柒都唔知，靠就靠旗手等等，有得睇住點做+趕音引導，團結分都起碼有。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">（後方補裝補彈）</span></span><br />\n：親愛的和理非，與其企喺度怕，倒不如真係做返啲野，身邊有啲咩執起有用，哪怕一舊磚，傳上去，用少少時間整舊水彈，傳上去，見到邊度有rb拆撚左佢來用，分分鐘係個關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n我相信我地咁多人，我地一定做到啲野，從中學習，唔可以比班死狗一個個咁拉撚走哂我地既手足。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">For Hong Kong</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求   缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家今日盡力打好十一宜一場仗"},{"pid":"f37dd78526ee9a72104cc50056b0757181b23f43","tid":1610372,"uid":262997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:15:08.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以幫我推下"},{"pid":"db4a105eb4182bffa99167482c4b6eaa348b800c","tid":1610372,"uid":262997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:15:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c178fbd4ed051222467446f60aa5f034134fe130","tid":1610372,"uid":262997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:15:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af96157cd2f9fdad5e2d9e9290cad7c90b4ef0a3","tid":1610372,"uid":262997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:15:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74348200aece89041994eaee5b55ce68ff5bf4ca","tid":1610372,"uid":262997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:16:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"687683a485d37d4e57dff34ac2e0072ed84dc01d","tid":1610372,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:27:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a066186c00b0c61d6634d3c8bf51c349a90763a0","tid":1610372,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:28:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe9228b0ff615ce2bf4a6bd6bf077e75015640f1","tid":1610372,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"45209c47971e7ba850202498780dfea694801bb5","tid":1610372,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:28:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66f623080386c289b154b6d08233e0b54432644a","tid":1610372,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:30:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8b3f603e1197efa8028a3a7db807af51894bd39","tid":1610372,"uid":48427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5b82059cce2aeb3c33e915b738744134447262","tid":1610372,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:30:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50deaaf029b6c20d418b5c788beb7e20e7e2f28f","tid":1610372,"uid":48427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re